## 

# CNvalidity
CNvalidity <- function(dat, clusters){
    CNvalidity0 <- function(dat, clusters, index = NULL){ #CH, H, KLCNvalidity0
    # index
    if(!is.element(index, c("CH", "H", "KL"))){
        stop("index")
    }
    N <- ncol(clusters) - 2 #
    d <- ncol(dat) #
    value <- data.frame(cluster.n = names(clusters)[2:(ncol(clusters)-1)], numeric(N)) #
    colnames(value)[2] <- index #(CH, H, KL)
    W <- function(X){ #W
        X <- as.matrix(X)
        V <- X-(rep(1, nrow(X)) %*% t(colMeans(X))) #
        W <- t(V) %*% V
        return(W)
    }
    from <- as.numeric(names(clusters)[2]) #
    to <- as.numeric(names(clusters)[(ncol(clusters) - 1)]) #
    for(i in from:to){#i
        # dat0-dati,i+1,i-1
        dat0 <- data.frame(dat, cluster1 = factor(clusters[, names(clusters) == as.character(i)]), 
            cluster2 = factor(clusters[, names(clusters) == as.character(i + 1)]), 
            cluster3 = factor(clusters[, names(clusters) == as.character(i - 1)]))
        Ws1 <- by(data = dat0[, 1:d], INDICES = dat0$cluster1, FUN = W) #i
        Ww1 <- Reduce(f = "+", Ws1) #i()
        if(index == "CH"){
            indexname <- "Calinski & Harabasz index"
            Z  <- Reduce(f = rbind, by(data = dat0[, 1:d],INDICES = dat0$cluster1, FUN = colMeans)) #i(id)
            ZZ <- Z - rep(1, i) %*% t(colMeans(dat0[, 1:d])) #Z(id)
            Nc <- diag(table(dat0$cluster1))#i
            Wb <- t(ZZ) %*% Nc %*% ZZ #i
            indexvalue <- (sum(diag((Wb))) / (i - 1))/(sum(diag((Ww1))) / (nrow(dat0) - i)) #CH
        }else if(index == "H"){
            indexname <- "Hartigan index"
            Ws2 <- by(data = dat0[, 1:d], INDICES = dat0$cluster2, FUN = W) #i+1
            Ww2 <- Reduce(f = "+", Ws2) #i+1()
            indexvalue <- (sum(diag((Ww1))) / sum(diag((Ww2))) - 1) * (nrow(dat0) - i - 1) #H
            if(i == from){ #diffH-1H
                Ws3 <- by(data = dat0[, 1:d], INDICES = dat0$cluster3, FUN = W)#i-1
                Ww3 <- Reduce(f = "+", Ws3) #i-1()       
                indexvalue_sub <- (sum(diag((Ww3))) / sum(diag((Ww1))) - 1 ) * (nrow(dat0) - (i - 1) - 1) #diffH
            }
        }else if(index == "KL"){
            indexname <- "Krzanowski & Lai index"
            Ws2 <- by(data = dat0[, 1:d], INDICES = dat0$cluster2, FUN = W)#i+1
            Ww2 <- Reduce(f = "+", Ws2) #i+1()
            Ws3 <- by(data = dat0[, 1:d], INDICES = dat0$cluster3, FUN = W)#i-1
            Ww3 <- Reduce(f = "+", Ws3) #i-1()
            DIFF1 <- sum(diag((Ww3))) * (i - 1) ^ (2 / d) - sum(diag((Ww1))) * (i) ^ (2 / d) #KL
            DIFF2 <- sum(diag((Ww1))) * (i) ^ (2 / d) - sum(diag((Ww2))) * (i + 1) ^ (2 / d) #KL
            indexvalue <- abs(DIFF1 / DIFF2) #KL
        }       
        value[value[, "cluster.n"] == as.character(i), 2] <- indexvalue #
    }

    if(index == "H"){
        #value-HdiffH
        value <- data.frame(value, diffH = c(-1 * diff(c(indexvalue_sub, value[, index]))))
    }
    return(value)
    }
    #CNvalidity0
    CHindex <- CNvalidity0(dat = dat, clusters = clusters, index = "CH") 
     Hindex <- CNvalidity0(dat = dat, clusters = clusters, index = "H") 
    KLindex <- CNvalidity0(dat = dat, clusters = clusters, index = "KL")
    indices <- merge(merge(CHindex, Hindex, by = "cluster.n", sort = FALSE), KLindex, by = "cluster.n", sort = FALSE)
    return(indices)
}
# 
from <- 1; to <- 11
clabel <- function(x){factor(cutree(ysi.out, k=x))}
clusters <- data.frame(lapply(from:to, clabel))
names(clusters) <- from:to

K

INTP.KM <- function(dat, ncluster){ #
    M <- nrow(dat) #
    center.all <- apply(dat, 2, mean) #
    DVATmat <- as.matrix((dat - rep(1, M) %*% t(center.all))) #
    DTC0 <- diag(DVATmat %*% t(DVATmat)) #
    INTP <- matrix(0, ncluster, ncol(dat)) #
    dat.ordered <- dat[order(DTC0), ] #
    for(i in 1:ncluster){
        INTP[i, ]<-unlist(dat.ordered[1 + (i - 1) * floor(M / ncluster), , drop = FALSE]) #
    }
    return(INTP)
}

#
INTP <- INTP.KM(dat=ysi, ncluster=3)
(ysi.out2 <- kmeans(x=ysi, centers=INTP))
